{"tid":882189,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"向互聯網巨擘開刀 英2020年開徵「數碼服務稅」","createTime":"2018-10-30T03:53:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T08:11:12.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e00a66badc83c459bbe40ac3ec7bee6188982c89","tid":882189,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T03:53:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181030/large/1540852628_7e47.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181030%2Flarge%2F1540852628_7e47.jpg&h=d3e22337&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英國政府周一發表財政預算案，宣佈2020年開徵新稅項，向互聯網巨擘開刀。<br />\n財相夏文達（Philip Hammond）表示，「數碼服務稅」是按特定數碼平台經營模式在英國產生的營業額徵收，稅率2%，形容是對象範圍「狹窄」的稅項，確保只有具規模的科技巨擘要交稅，而初創企業不受影響，只有全球營業額達5億鎊（50.21億港元）的企業要繳稅。<br />\n新稅項2020年4月起生效，預計令英國庫房每年進賬4億鎊（40.16億港元）。<br />\n受「數碼服務稅」消息影響，亞馬遜、Google、Facebook、Netflix、蘋果等科網龍頭股價都下跌。<br />\n英國科技業界擔心，「數碼服務稅」可能會嚇跑科網巨擘在英國的投資。<br />\n路透社／英國《每日郵報》  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181030/58851576\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181030%2F58851576&d=79EXsNWsPp3oP0Kg6YFLVu9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=57ac3c7e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181030%2F58851576&h=447a6aea\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181030/58851576</a>"},{"pid":"b4af6d64440b046e142ff01692a0cb883ec623d1","tid":882189,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T04:14:15.000Z","msg":"應份啦 將稅收再分配係社會到"},{"pid":"8950d4bcd10df66ab115c2c656656afd96f3ec87","tid":882189,"uid":29063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T05:01:13.000Z","msg":"佢地佔用左唔少網絡流量，係應該要收返啲改善網絡建設"},{"pid":"007b32653379fd563819a482e0a6202ea15078ff","tid":882189,"uid":10125,"li